     <script type="text/javascript">
      function clearExperienceStats() {
            $j("#experienceGraph").empty();
            $j("#trimLabel").empty();
            $j("#interiorRank").empty();
            $j("#exteriorRank").empty();
        }

        function createColor(elementID, rank) {
            $j.each(rank, function(i, obj) {
                $j(elementID).append('<li><span>' + obj.percent + '%</span><br /><img src="' + obj.value + '" alt="" /></li>');
            });
        }

        function createTrimGraph(trimRank) {

            var trimSize = $j(trimRank).size();

            var bestIndex = 0;

            $j.each(trimRank, function(i, obj) {
                    var h = (obj.percent / 100) * 188;
                    ++bestIndex;
                    if (trimSize == 2 && i == 1) {
                        bestIndex += 1;
                    }
                    $j("#experienceGraph").append('<div class="best' + bestIndex + '" style="height:' + h + 'px">&nbsp;</div>');
                    $j("#trimLabel").append('<li class="best' + bestIndex + '" style="height:' + h + 'px;">' +
                        '<span class="percent">' + obj.percent + '%</span>' +
                        '<span class="name">' + obj.value + '</span>' +
                        '<span class="help"></span>' +
                        '</li>');
                }
            );
        }

        function createExperienceStats(data) {
            if (data) {
                clearExperienceStats();
            } else {
                Comment.hideLoadingImage("#experienceLoadingBox");
                return false;
            }
            createTrimGraph(data.trimRank);
            createColor("#interiorRank", data.interiorRank);
            createColor("#exteriorRank", data.exteriorRank);
            Comment.hideLoadingImage("#experienceLoadingBox");
        };

        function getExperienceStats() {

            Comment.showLoadingImage("#experienceLoadingBox");

            $j.ajaxSetup({ dataType: "json" });
            var result = $j.post(
                "/wcm/gt/front/sns/getExperienceStats.do", {
                    wwn_country_code: $j("#wwn_country_code").val(),
                    modelCode: $j("#modelCode").val()
                }, function(data, textStatus) {
                    createExperienceStats(data);
                }
            );
            result.error(function(error) {
                Comment.ajaxError(error);
            });

            result.complete(function(co) {
                Comment.hideLoadingImage("#experienceLoadingBox");
            });
        }

        function popupExperienceStats() {
            var w = parseInt(($j(window).width() - 600) / 2);
            $j(".layer_experience").css("left", w).fadeIn();
            getExperienceStats();
        }
     </script>

       <img alt="Trim" src="/Img/Hyundai/gfx/layer_experience_title_trim.png"/>

      </div>
      <div class="graph" id="experienceGraph">
       <!-- style의 height 값은 Best3의 %값과 동일한 것이 아닙니다. -->
       <!-- 55(a)/25(b)/15(c)에 대한 백분률 값을 다시 계산한 후, 188을 곱해 주시면 됩니다. 188은 고정임 -->
       <!-- best1의 height: x=a*188/(a+b+c) -->
       <!-- best2의 height: y=b*188/(a+b+c) -->
       <!-- best3의 height: z=188-x-y -->
       <!-- 3가지 합쳐서 188이 되도록 마지막 값은 100에서 위의 두 값을 빼 줍니다. -->
       <!-- Style, height is not the value of the% is the same as the value of Best3. -->
       <!-- 55 (a) / 25 (b) / 15 (c) for the percentage recalculated after the value, multiplied by 188, please. 188 is fixed -->
       <!-- Best1 height: x = a * 188 / (a + b + c) -->
       <!-- Best2 height: y = b * 188 / (a ​​+ b + c) -->
       <!-- Best3 height: z = 188-x-y ->
                Combining three kinds of 188 to the last value from 100 subtract the two values ​​of the above shows. -->
      </div>
      <ul class="trim_best3" id="trimLabel">

                            var heightOfIframe = Math.max(
                                Math.max(D.body.scrollHeight, D.documentElement.scrollHeight),
                                Math.max(D.body.offsetHeight, D.documentElement.offsetHeight),
                                Math.max(D.body.clientHeight, D.documentElement.clientHeight)

                            if (iFrames[i].contentWindow.document.body.offsetHeight > 200) {

                                //ie 8 wont resize properly when new elements are added to the form. Increase offset height so controls wont be hidden
                                if (JQuery.browser.msie) {
                                    if (JQuery.browser.version >= 8 && JQuery.browser.version < 9) {
                                        heightOfIframe = iFrames[i].contentWindow.document.body.offsetHeight + 20;

                            } else {
                                iFrames[i].style.height = heightOfIframe + 'px';
                            }
                        }

        <script type="text/javascript">
         $j(function () {
        var controlId = "HyundaiPopUpCampaign_ctl05";
        var contextId = "#" + controlId;
        var useCampaignPrefix = "False" == "True";
        if (!useCampaignPrefix) {
            $j(document).delegate(contextId + " .hoverinfo", "mouseenter mouseleave", function (event) {
                event.preventDefault();
                var infobox = $j(this).find('.infobox');
                var marginleft = ($j(infobox).outerWidth() / 2 - $j(this).width() / 2) * -1;
                var margintop = ($j(infobox).outerHeight() + $j(this).height() + 10) * -1;
                $j(infobox).css({ 'margin-left': marginleft + 'px', 'margin-top': margintop + 'px' });
                $j(this).toggleClass('open');
            });
        }
        else
        {
            $j(document).delegate("#campaignpopup .hoverinfo", "mouseenter mouseleave", function (event) {
                event.preventDefault();
                $j(this).toggleClass('open');
            });
        }
        var hasSplit = false;
        var fromBase = "False" == "True";
        var disclaimerData = "";

        var dataReady = function () {

            var generateDisclaimerPart = function (text) {
                var context = $j(contextId);

                if (text.length > 10 && text.indexOf("FN") > -1) {
                    var myRe = /{.*?}/g;
                    var footnoteCount = disclaimerData.disclaimer.text.match(/FN/g).length;
                    for (var i = 0; i < footnoteCount; i++) {
                        var res = myRe.exec(disclaimerData.disclaimer.text)[0];

                        var fn = res.split(':')[0].replace("{", "");
                        if (text.indexOf(fn) > -1) {
                            var visibleText = res.split(':')[1].replace("}", "");
                            var hoverText = disclaimerData.footnotes[fn];

                            var hoverboxTemplate = $j("#hoverinfoTemplate", context).clone();
                            var infobox = $j("#infoboxTemplate .infobox", context).clone();
                            var infoarrow = $j("#infoArrowTemplate .infoboxarrow", context).clone();

                            infobox.text(hoverText);
                            infobox.append(infoarrow);

                            hoverboxTemplate.find(".hoverinfo", context).text(visibleText);
                            hoverboxTemplate.find(".hoverinfo", context).append(infobox);

                            text = text.replace(res, hoverboxTemplate.html());
                        }
                    }
                }
                return text;
            };
            var context = $j(contextId);

            //As a default, there is shown a disclaimer text. If we have a custom disclaimer, set it up.
            if (disclaimerData !== undefined) {

                var extrainfo = $j(".extrainfo label[for=extrainfo]", context);
                extrainfo.html("");
                //var disclaimerData = JSON.parse($j('div[disclaimer]').attr('disclaimer'));

                //var text = disclaimerData.disclaimer.text;

                hasSplit = disclaimerData.disclaimer.text.indexOf('|') > -1;
                //Handle 'read more', it there is an '|' 
                if (hasSplit) {
                    var disclaimer = "<div class=\"readMoreFirst\">";
                    disclaimer += generateDisclaimerPart(disclaimerData.disclaimer.text.split('|')[0]);
                    disclaimer += $j("#readMoreDisclaimerLinkTemplate").html();
                    disclaimer += "</div>";
                    
                    disclaimer += "<div class=\"readMoreSecond\">";
                    disclaimer += generateDisclaimerPart(disclaimerData.disclaimer.text.replace("|", ""));
                    disclaimer += $j("#readLessDisclaimerLinkTemplate").html();
                    disclaimer += "</div>";
                    $j(extrainfo).html(disclaimer);
                } else {
                    $j(extrainfo).html(generateDisclaimerPart(disclaimerData.disclaimer.text));
                }


            }
            if (hasSplit) {
                $j(".readMoreSecond", context).hide();

                $j("#disclaimerTextContainer").delegate(".readMoreDisclaimerLink", "click", function (event) {
                    event.preventDefault();
                    var wrapper = $j(this).parents(".extrainfo:first");
                    $j(".readMoreFirst", wrapper).hide();
                    $j(".readMoreDisclaimerLink", wrapper).hide();
                    $j(".readLessDisclaimerLink", wrapper).show();
                    $j(".readMoreSecond", wrapper).show();
                    parent.$j("iframe").height(parent.$j("iframe").height() + $j(".readMoreSecond", wrapper).height());
                });
                $j("#disclaimerTextContainer").delegate(".readLessDisclaimerLink", "click", function (event) {
                    event.preventDefault();
                    var wrapper = $j(this).parents(".extrainfo:first");
                    $j(".readMoreFirst", wrapper).show();
                    $j(".readMoreDisclaimerLink", wrapper).show();
                    $j(".readLessDisclaimerLink", wrapper).hide();
                    $j(".readMoreSecond", wrapper).hide();
                    parent.$j("iframe").height(parent.$j("iframe").height() - $j(".readMoreSecond", wrapper).height());
                });
            }
        };


        if (fromBase) {
            disclaimerData = JSON.parse($j("#CustomDisclaimer").attr("disclaimer"));
            dataReady();
        } else {
            if ($j("div[disclaimer]").length != 0 && !useCampaignPrefix) {
                disclaimerData = JSON.parse($j('div[disclaimer]').attr('disclaimer'));
                dataReady();
            }
            else {
                var iframeReady = function (counter) {
                    try
                    {
                        if ($j("#campaigniframe").contents().find("div[disclaimer]").length == 0 && counter < 100) {
                            counter++;
                            setTimeout(iframeReady, 200, counter);
                        }
                        else {
                            var disclaimerText = $j("#campaigniframe").contents().find("div[disclaimer]").attr("disclaimer");
                            if (typeof disclaimerText === 'undefined' || disclaimerText.length == 0)
                                disclaimerText = $j(document.getElementById('campaigniframe').contentWindow.document).find("div[disclaimer]").attr("disclaimer");
                            if (typeof disclaimerText === 'undefined') {
                                counter++;
                                setTimeout(iframeReady, 200, counter);
                            }
                            else {
                                disclaimerData = JSON.parse(disclaimerText);
                                dataReady();
                                $j(document).resize();
                            }
                        }
                    }
                    catch(err)
                    {
                        window.console && console.log(err.message);
                        counter++;
                        setTimeout(iframeReady, 200, counter);
                    }
                };
                iframeReady(0);
            }
        }

    });

    $j(function () {
        var checkbox = $j("#extrainfo");
        $j(checkbox).prop("checked", false);
    });
        </script>
